article.section:
Attribute Definitions
Each attribute list in DocBook V5.0 is defined by its own pattern. To change the list of attributes available on an element, only that pattern need be redefined. To remove all the attributes, that pattern can be redefined as empty. <<<<<<< .mine
The following attribute definitions have been added to the Publishers schema:
